  "excerpt": "<p><p>It’s finally here! My recap post with a TON of photos from the 2016 Philly Flower Show! We went on March 7th, so I know I’m a little late- thanks for being so patient. 🙂 The theme this year was “Explore America” and was honoring 100 Years of the National Parks Service. Check out all the […]</p></p>",
  "content": "<p>It’s finally here! My recap post with a TON of photos from the 2016 Philly Flower Show! We went on March 7th, so I know I’m a little late- thanks for being so patient. 🙂 The theme this year was “Explore America” and was honoring 100 Years of the National Parks Service. Check out all the photos I took below!</p><p>The Flower Show is my favorite annual date with the Husband. We’ve gone every year since we met, so this was the 7th one we attended! The theme this year was probably my least favorite so far, as most of the floral displays were indicative of National Parks that lack in colorful flora and center around trees and underbrush with greens and browns. The displays themselves were put together well, but I prefer things overflowing with colorful flowers. It was still a very nice day, and I did manage to take some great photos!</p><p>First up was the Butterfly Experience! I had a few friends land on me, while Husband had even more! They were really digging his shirt.</p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1123.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1125.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1129.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1134.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p>I was afraid to move at all with this guy sitting right above my purse!\n Then this pretty girl landed on my arm too, so I was trapped! Trapped by butterflies isn’t such a bad thing.</p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1136.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1170.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1156.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1157.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1159.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1164.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1168.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p>After visiting with the butterflies, we headed into the main showroom to check out all the exhibits.</p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1184.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1185.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1191.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1186.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-0008.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-0005.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-0004.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1193.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1197.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1199.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1200.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1203.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1208.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1211.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1209.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1216.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1217.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1219.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1222.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1228.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1230.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1234.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><figure id=\"attachment_7915\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7915\"><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1224.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7915\"><p>We threw in some pennies and made some wishes!</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1235.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1236.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1238.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1242.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1245.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1243.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p>One display had a chalkboard to write on, so of course I added our initials!</p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1248.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1247.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p>Love the Autumn color theme in this display!</p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1249.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1250.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1251.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1252.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1253.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1254.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1258.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1260.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1263.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1264.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1268.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1269.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1261.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1271.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1273.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1275.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1272.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1277.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1278.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p><figure id=\"attachment_7947\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7947\"><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1282.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-7947\"><p>Can you spot the owl?</p></figcaption></figure><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1284.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p><p>It is quite hard to tell from these photos, but this is the ceiling in a little enclosure in one of the exhibits. It was so pretty in person!</p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1285.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1288.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1290.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"735\"></p><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1293.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"735\"></p><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1291.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1306.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1299.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1300.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1302.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1305.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1307.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1309.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p>This next exhibit wasn’t skinny and weird at the top like the photo shows- it was all the same width. That’s just the pano doing it’s weird thing!</p><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1314.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"2112\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1315.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1317.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1320.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p>I really enjoyed the window displays. It makes me want to redo my front window!</p><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1323.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1327.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1328.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1330.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1331.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1338.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1339.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p>I also wish I could have a front porch like some of these amazing displays!</p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1342.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1341.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1343.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1347.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p>I tried to take photos of all the mini dioramas, but the glare on the glass was horrible. At least I was able to snap a few, including one depicting an apparent nude beach! Hah!</p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1373.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1374.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1375.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1391.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1382.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1383.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p>I always enjoy the pressed flower artworks! They are so creative and pretty.</p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1394.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1396.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1395.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1397.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1407.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1406.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1408.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1410.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><p>And let’s not forget this one by an elementary school student!</p><p><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1411.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p><div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1429.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1430.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\">\n        </div></div><figure id=\"attachment_8000\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8000\"><img class=\"size-full post__image\" src=\"/posts/2016-philly-flower-show-recap/img-1431.jpg\" alt=\"2016 Philly Flower Show Recap on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8000\"><p>Good bye, Mr. Bald Eagle! It was good seeing you!</p></figcaption></figure><p>That’s it for my photos of the Philadelphia Flower Show! I hope you enjoyed them. I will be sure to post again next year!</p><p>Which photo was your favorite? Did you attend the show this year?</p>",
